metadata.name: World Cup Collectors Editions #1
metadata.description: World Cup Collectors Editions is an NFT collection of 522 Tokens representing the 32 teams of the 2022 FIFA World Cup, held in Qatar. The holders of the NFTs representing the winning team will receive 50% of the WCCE revenues, split among all holders, with the holder of the Rare for the winning team receiving a double share. All winnings will be received within 24 hours of the closing of the World Cup Final Match.
